COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 6:31PM PT yesterday, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.4 thousand have died.

In the last day, 383 new infections were reported and 8 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 39.7 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 78% have their 1st shot and 41.4% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 9.1 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~17 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Sep-28 and fully vaccinated by Aug-22. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
